<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ha">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Bootstrap Shafina</title>
    <style>
        body { background-color: #f8f9fa; font-family: sans-serif; padding: 30px; }
        .container { background-color: white; max-width: 450px; margin: 50px auto; padding: 40px; text-align: center; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        .text-primary { color: #0d6efd; font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .text-muted { color: #6c757d; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; }
        /* Sabbin launuka na maballan Bootstrap */
        .btn-danger { background-color: #dc3545; color: white; border: none; width: 100%; padding: 12px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 15px; cursor: pointer; }
        .btn-warning { background-color: #ffc107; color: #212529; border: none; width: 100%; padding: 12px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 15px; cursor: pointer; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <!-- Mun canza wannan zuwa kalar ja ta hanyar jigon Danger -->
        <div class="text-primary" style="color: #dc3545;">Koyi Launukan Bootstrap!</div>
        <div class="text-muted">Gobe za mu koyi yadda ake saka maballai masu launuka daban-daban a jere ba tare da sun gauraye ba.</div>
        
        <!-- Maballin Farko: Ja (Danger) -->
        <button class="btn-danger">Wannan Maballin Danger Ne (Ja)</button>
        
        <!-- Maballin Biyu: Dorawa (Warning) -->
        <button class="btn-warning">Wannan Maballin Warning Ne (Dorawa)</button>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
